Name: Wavecat Pillow
Desc: The seventh product of the smash hit Momo Friends collaboration line-up! This Wavecat-shaped pillow is this year's third most popular bedding item.

Name: Peroro Wheel
Desc: The ninth product of the smash hit Momo Friends collaboration line-up. This Peroro-shaped exercise equipment is this year's most popular fitness accessory!

Name: A-Pods Pro
Desc: Wireless earphones that are all the rage among Kivotos students. A bit expensive to buy on a tight budget, since they retail for about three months of part-time pay.

Name: The Love Which Couldn't Be- Beauty Found in What's Not Allowed -
Desc:
The latest work from the popular romance novelist who wrote "Koi About Love"!
Delve into a dizzying tale of forbidden love!

Name: Hitgirls Gaming Magazine
Desc: Stay up to date on the latest releases, strategies for classic games, new gaming merch and everything in betweenthis magazine covers it all!

Name: Cherry-Rose Lip Gloss
Desc:
A lip gloss with a subtle yet striking hue.
It's one of the hottest selling items among young ladies interested in beauty and grooming.

Name: Glassy Glow BB Cream
Desc:
A hit product from the luxury cosmetics brand "Samuela."
This BB cream brightens and evens out skin tone and provides a natural finish for a healthy glow.

Name: Military Camo Foundation Trio
Desc:
A hit product from luxury cosmetics brand "Samuela."
It provides lightweight camouflage capabilities that melt into your skin! Be camo-ready any time, any place!

Name: Fine Cookie Set
Desc: A luxury cookie set from Schrodinger's, famed for its rich, buttery sweetness. There's often a fifty percent chance that it contains something other than cookies.

Name: Guns, Charm, and Zeal
Desc:
Guns, charm, and zeal!
The bestselling book of the year investigates and analyzes the origins and roots of Kivotos pop culture.

Name: Astronomical Telescope
Desc: This astronomical telescope is deemed the standard for hobbyists by the Kivotos Astronomy Observatory.

Name: Gamegirl Color Replica
Desc:
"Life is your arcade!"
Go wild with retromania with this vintage reproduction of the classic Gamegirl Color.

Name: MX-Ration C-Type Dessert Flavor
Desc: Calories equal Combat Power!

Name: Matcha Ramune
Desc:
A matcha-flavored carbonated soft drink.
Green and refreshing!

Name: Jellies Cushion
Desc: The star of "Fruitjellies" is back! In cushion form! They've managed to recreate the concept of a jelly eating another jelly of the same color in great detail!

Name: Extraordinary Cottontail Detective- Case of the Misty Hot Spring Slide -
Desc: Whenever there's a case, these snow-white bunny ears are sure to crack it! Volume 3 of the Extraordinary Cottontail Detective series! The stage is set at the hot springs!

Name: Ring Bit
Desc: "Make fitness fun with games!" This exercise equipment uses an O-ring to make working out at home easy and fun whether for strength training or slimming down!

Name: Buried Treasure Map
Desc:
There's treasure out there somewhere!
A map of the sites where the three great gold treasures of Kivotos are supposed to be buried.

Name: Cosplayer Coke-Bottle Glasses
Desc: Wear these to instantly look like a genius! Einstein's got nothing on you (in appearance, anyway)!  Note: Wearing these will not raise your IQ.

Name: World's Most Useless Gadget
Desc: Absolutely useless, but cute! Still, it's completely pointless. And yet, its cuteness totally makes up for it! This trinket is among the top five best toys to give to a special friend.

Name: Teddy Bear with Bow
Desc:
An ordinary but absolutely darling teddy bear.
A popular product among students who love all things cute and adorable.

Name: Movie Ticket
Desc: "Snuggle up with your special someone and watch a movie!" This movie ticket is accepted at any theater, and admits two people!

Name: 30-Color Paint Set
Desc:
A professional paint set with tubes in a variety of thirty colors.
Time to go and paint the whole wide world!

Name: Classical Poetry Anthology
Desc:
An anthology of classical poetry. Very classy.
Provides all the sophistication of classical literature right at your fingertips.

Name: Cute Dishware Set
Desc:
A dishware set painted with adorable animal characters.
This product has made the top ten list of best selling dishware in Kivotos year after year.

Name: Brain Teaser Puzzle Cube
Desc: "If you can solve this, then you deserve your place at Millennium!" A puzzle cube for advanced users certified by the Millennium Science School.

Name: Large Whole Cake
Desc:
The mere sight of this massive cake is enough to satisfy the senses.
Its caloric info is detailed underneath.

Name: Luxury Buffet Ticket
Desc:
This ticket grants access to a luxury buffet operated by the best chef in all of Kivotos.
As you might expect, it's very expensive.

Name: Potted Bug-Eating Plant
Desc: A potted plant that's popular among those with eccentric taste. Apparently, the way it devours insects is cuter than you'd think.

Name: Extravagant Gilded Jar of Greed
Desc:
An obviously exorbitant-looking jar gilt with gold leaf.
Watch out for counterfeits!

Name: Wind-Up Music Box
Desc:
An fancy solid-wood music box with vintage charm.
Very popular among collectors.

Name: Embroidered Handkerchief
Desc: An exquisitely embroidered handkerchief.

Name: Encyclopedia
Desc: From "that tie thing" for tying bread bags to "the grass thing" that goes in bento boxes, everything you ever wanted to read about can be found right here.

Name: Health Food Supplement
Desc:
Feel rejuvenated with just one bite!
This supplement is the perfect gift for your special someone.

Name: Summer Tube
Desc:
It's summer! To the beach!
A safety device for swimmers of all experience levels. Ready for anything with its cute and fancy design!
TOP3

Name: Hatsune Miku Photo Card
Desc: A special photo card distributed at Miku's Kivotos Live Concert. They have become rare pieces of merch that any Miku fan wants to own.

Name: Shiny Bouquet
Desc:
A crystal bouquet perfect for giving to a special someone.
It sparkles like a kaleidoscope in the light.

Name: Mission Data 1: D Type
Desc: Data used to analyze Decagrammaton.

Name: Secret Tech Sheet Fragment
Desc: A fragment of Tech Notes containing tactical secrets. Can be restored using the tailor-made function of the Crafting Chamber.

Name: Secret Tech Sheet

Name: Event Points
Desc: These points are earned each time you progress in an event. The more you earn, the greater the variety of rewards you can receive.

Name: Kitsune Senbei
Desc: The iconic street food of Hyakkiyako's festivals. Each crispy bite is full of melt-in-your-mouth deliciousness!

Name: Tanuki Okonomiyaki
Desc: It's not a Hyakkiyako festival without this beloved treat! The raccoon drawn in mayo is adorable.

Name: Sakura Daifuku
Desc: The steadiest-selling dessert of Hyakkiyako's Momoyodou tea house. Its subtle yet rich sweetness makes it a classic.

Name: Cherino Matryoshka
Desc: A matryoshka made in Cherino's majestic likeness. Something rattles inside when you shake it.

Name: Cherenka Chocolate
Desc: An affordable milk chocolate made by the Red Winter School Lunch Club. It's sweet and soft, but Red Winter students find it difficult to eat when hardened by the cold.

Name: Mustache Crepe
Desc: A sweet and soft crepe sold throughout the Red Winter Academy. Also known as a blini. Cherino's approval is required to add the mustache-shaped cream decoration.

Name: Red Mustache Medal
Desc: A luxurious gold medal with precious stones awarded to students Cherino recognizes as worthy. Most keep it stored in their desks due to its sharp edges.

Name: Event Points
Desc: These points are earned each time you progress in an event. The more you earn, the greater the variety of rewards you can receive.

Name: Beach Volleyball
Desc: A cute beach volleyball.

Name: Beach Shack Meal Ticket
Desc: A shabby meal ticket that can be used at the Beach Shack.

Name: Weird Fireworks
Desc: Has the shape of a cute missile.

Name: Ice Cooler
Desc: An ice cooler that can store fruit and drinks at a cool temperature. It's also effective at storing temperature-sensitive firearms.

Name: Sand Play Set
Desc: A Sand Play Set with tools for building simple sand castles. Cement and rebar not included.

Name: Beach Chair
Desc: A modern beach chair with soft fabric laid atop wood. It's waterproof, allowing you to use it with ease at the beach.

Name: Parasol Table
Desc: A solid wood table with a sunshade parasol. A proper lady can't miss tea time, even at the beach.

Name: Water Play Equipment
Desc: Full-fledged watersports equipment with a snorkel and oxygen tank. Not recommend for depths exceeding 50m.

Name: Sailing Board
Desc: A board with sails attached to the hull to increase acceleration. It's easy to balance, making it perfect for beginners.

Name: Gehenna Supply Box
Desc:
Supplies prepared by the Prefect Team before summer boot camp.
They'll help you train! Don't worry, they're all winners!

Name: GRS Grilled Corn
Desc:
Grilled corn prepared by the Gourmet Research Society.
Curated to the tastes of its memberstastiness not guaranteed!

Name: Thug Summer Shades
Desc:
Seized by the Prefect Team from a troublemaker at the beach.
Signs of a helpless struggle remain.

Name: Splashy Helmet
Desc:
Seized by the Prefect Team from a Splashy Helmet Gang hoodlum in the beachside slums.
Signs of a futile struggle remain.

Name: Event Points
Desc: These points are earned each time you progress in an event. The more you earn, the greater the variety of rewards you can receive.

Name: Turtle Mushroom
Desc: An exotic mushroom that grows naturally throughout the Shanhaijing district. Contrary to how it looks, its firm texture and great taste make it a delicacy.

Name: Black Bamboo Shoot
Desc: Black bamboo shoots growing in the gardens of Genryumon. Difficult to obtain due to strict management of Genryumon officers.

Name: Ginseng Doll
Desc: A human-shaped root herb found deep in the mountains of Shanhaijing. It's said to have effects that prolong your life or make you younger.

Name: Chocolate Coin
Desc: One of the famous snacks of the Golden Fleece. Not a real coin, but popular among students because of its sweet taste.

Name: Rabbit Sticker
Desc: A rabbit-shaped sticker used by students. They don't really mean anything. They're easy to make, so most students make their own.

Name: Boarding Pass
Desc: A boarding pass for the Golden Fleece. Even after boarding, it is best to carry it at all times since it's often needed functions and events.

Name: Dice
Desc: Dice like those often found aboard ships. Although they're a simple toy, they are sometimes used to resolve conflicts between students.

Name: Event Points
Desc: These points are earned each time you progress in an event. The more you earn, the greater the variety of rewards you can receive.

Name: Hot Spring Towel
Desc: Basic towels provided by Hot Springs Resort No. 227. They're made from rough materials and may cause damage to the skin.

Name: Mustache Shampoo
Desc: President Cherino's favorite Red Winter Academy special shampoo. Contrary to the name, it's not suitable for washing a mustache.

Name: Capybara Bath Bomb
Desc: A bath bomb in the shape of a capybara. When you put it in water, it melts and gives off a subtle citrus scent.

Name: New Year's Lucky Pouch
Desc: A lucky pouch prepared by the Kurokame Gang for New Year's. No one knows what's inside until they open it up. There's actually some pretty good stuff in there.

Name: Peroro Kagami Mochi
Desc: Kagami mochi made in collaboration with the super popular mascot, Peroro, by the money-hungry Kurokame Gang. For decoration only and cannot be eaten.

Name: Kurokame Gang Ema
Desc: Ema sold at the Kurokame Gang's New Year's event. There's a rumor that its effect will increase if you give an offering and make a wish. That's why they're overpriced at 5,000 yen each.

Name: New Year Omikuji Token
Desc: Token required to pick out a New Year's omikuji. Something the Kurokame Gang created to increase profits. Prizes are awarded according to the results of the fortune-telling.
